A Meru assembly clerk Gideon Thuranira Ruciaka has died in a road accident at Kaaga in North Imenti. Thuranira was driving from Makutano to Maua. Police said Thuranira's vehicle veered off the road and rolled three times. He was rushed to Meru Teaching and Referral hospital where he was pronounced dead. Thuranira started working at the County Assembly in 2014 as a committee clerk. The car was towed to Meru police station and detained awaiting inspection. Click here for the latest political news